ve window treatment. Crafted from richly textured fabrics and elegantly<br\/>hungover windows, drapes provide exceptional privacy and superior light<br\/>blockage.<\/p><p>The performance of drapery depends greatly on the fabric's color and construction.<br\/>Generally, darker shades offer better light absorption, while denser, tightly<br\/>woven fabrics provide greater opacity. The tighter the weave and the heavier<br\/>the fabric, the more effective it becomes in blocking light and creating a<br\/>comfortable, private space.<\/p>","text_style":"body"}},"template--19880871690533__b5ea2b77-1bc2-4600-b14a-ec54814bf428-button-1":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"Schedule For Appointment","button_link":"shopify:\/\/pages\/get-a-quote"}}},"block_order":["template--19880871690533__b5ea2b77-1bc2-4600-b14a-ec54814bf428-heading-1","template--19880871690533__b5ea2b77-1bc2-4600-b14a-ec54814bf428-text-1","template--19880871690533__b5ea2b77-1bc2-4600-b14a-ec54814bf428-button-1"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/20942664755.png","height":"small","desktop_image_width":"small","layout":"image_first","desktop_content_position":"top","desktop_content_alignment":"left","content_layout":"no-overlap","color_scheme":"background-2","image_behavior":"none","mobile_content_alignment":"center","padding_top":12,"padding_bottom":12}},"d7af5d4d-8175-47ab-902b-c22d5a77efcc":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"template--19880871690533__d7af5d4d-8175-47ab-902b-c22d5a77efcc-heading-1":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"About Us","heading_size":"h1"}},"template--19880871690533__d7af5d4d-8175-47ab-902b-c22d5a77efcc-text-1":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>\"We are the country's best window fashion retailer.<br\/>We’ve steadily and consistently worked hard maintaining that goal ever since we started in a small 2-person showroom in the Philippines since 2008.\"<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["template--19880871690533__d7af5d4d-8175-47ab-902b-c22d5a77efcc-heading-1","template--198